\lim_{n \to \infty }\frac{n}{\ln\left ( \frac{3n}{10} \right )}
\lim_{n \to \infty }\frac{n}{\ln\left ( \frac{3n}{10} \right )}
=\lim_{n \to \infty }\frac{n}{\ln3+\log n-\log{10} }
\frac {\infty}{\infty}
\lim_{n \to \infty }\frac{n}{\ln\left ( \frac{3n}{10} \right )} =\lim_{n \to \infty }\frac{n}{\ln3+\log n-\log{10} } =\lim_{n \to \infty }\frac1{\frac 1n}=\lim_{n \to \infty } n=\infty
\ln\left ( \frac{3n}{10} \right )=m,n=\frac {10}3 e^m
m\to \infty
n\to \infty
\lim_{n \to \infty }\frac{n}{\ln\left ( \frac{3n}{10} \right )} =\frac{10}3\lim_{m \to \infty }\frac{e^m}m  =\frac{10}3\lim_{m \to \infty }\frac{1+\frac m{1!}+\frac {m^2}{2!}+\cdots }m
=\frac{10}3\cdot\lim_{m \to \infty }\{ \frac 1m +m+\frac m{2!}+\cdots\}=\infty 
